organic.title: Pediatric Cancer | Doernbecher Children's Hospital - OHSU
organic.snippet: OHSU Doernbecher Children's Hospital is a national leader in care for pediatric cancer. We treat childhood tumors, leukemia, lymphoma and more.

organic.title: Pediatric Cancer and Blood Disorders Team - OHSU
organic.snippet: Pediatric cancer care team. Our medical team includes national experts from the OHSU Knight Cancer Institute who specialize in treating children.

organic.title: Pediatric Oncology—Oregon Medical Services - Asante
organic.snippet: Asante maintains the only pediatric cancer center between San Francisco and Portland. We always work to keep families together. Find out more, here.

organic.title: Pediatric Oncology and Hematology - Providence
organic.snippet: We diagnose and treat children and teens with: Blood disorders, Bone tumors, Brain tumors, Hemophilia, Leukemia, Lymphoma, Solid tumors, Thrombosis.

organic.title: Oregon Oncology Specialists: Our Commitment to Excellence ...
organic.snippet: Oregon Oncology Specialists is a practice of Oregon Specialty Group, specializing in advanced treatments and compassionate care for more than 20 years.
